# Used by `sandcastle docker build-image --dockerfile .sandcastle/Dockerfile`,
# which uses the repo root as the build context. The Dockerfile only needs the
# dependency manifests, so exclude everything else (keeps the context tiny and
# avoids shipping library.db / artifacts / node_modules into the build).
*
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
# Frontend manifests for the pre-baked `npm ci` layer (.sandcastle/Dockerfile, added in #152).
# `*` also excludes the parent dirs, so walk down re-including each level, then the two files.
!apps
apps/*
!apps/visualizer
apps/visualizer/*
!apps/visualizer/frontend
apps/visualizer/frontend/*
!apps/visualizer/frontend/package.json
!apps/visualizer/frontend/package-lock.json
